// Dashboard
// Main dashboard view: sessions panel on the left and an items grid on the right in a SplitPane.
// Loads sessions and items via hooks; supports selecting, refreshing, and resizing panels.

FUNCTION RefreshIcon() -> ReactNode
  Renders a small circular arrow SVG icon used on the refresh button.

---

FUNCTION handleSessionClick(session)
  Sets the selected session via sessionStore/useSession.
  Navigates or updates URL to reflect the selected session.

---

FUNCTION handleItemClick(item)
  Opens the selected item in the appropriate editor/viewer via uiStore.

---

FUNCTION handlePanelResize(sizes)
  Persists the panel size percentages for the SplitPane layout.

---

FUNCTION handleRefresh()
  Triggers a data reload via useDataLoader and useSession.

---

FUNCTION Dashboard() -> ReactNode                                         EXPORT
  CALLS: useSession (useSession), useDataLoader (useDataLoader), useUIStore (uiStore), SplitPane (SplitPane), SessionCard (SessionCard), ItemGrid (ItemGrid)
  Renders a SplitPane: sessions list on the left, items grid on the right.
  Shows loading and error states for both panels.
  Provides a refresh button that calls handleRefresh.
